EU, IMF Back Portugal’s Plan on Tax Deductions, Diario Reports

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-04-27T06:52:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/eu-imf-back-portugal-s-plan-on-tax-deductions-diario-reports.html
International Monetary Fund  and
European Union officials back the Portuguese government’s plan
to end  tax deductions  for house purchases, Diario Economico
reported, without saying how it obtained the information.  Officials of the IMF, European Commission and  European
Central Bank  are in Lisbon preparing an aid plan for  Portugal 
following the government’s April 6 request for financial
assistance.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
